data.text:
Testimonials

Joining the Catherine McAuley School community was the best decision for our family! The teachers go above and beyond, the office staff always have a smile on their faces and we loved being greated by leadership each morning.

Melissa, Parent

Testimonials

We highly recommend Catherine McAuley School to anyone looking for a school with a small community feel, where no matter your background or learning needs, you are cared for.

Steven, Parent

Testimonials

Our boys have settled in so well and at all times, our children's health, wellbeing and education are a priority...not only to their teacher and the entire school community.

Karen, Parent

Testimonials

We love Catherine McAuley School and would recommend this school to anyone seeking a community where children are heard, respected and encouraged to reach their full potential.

Bindee, Parent

Testimonials

I like that all the teachers are kind and look after me. I like saying hello to everyone at the gate every morning and seeing my friends. I like being able to be student leader.

Hudson, Year 1 Student

Testimonials

I like being able to play soccer with my friends at recess and lunch. I enjoy doing mindfulness every day and learning my favorite subject math.

Tyson, Year 2 Student
